This Text Editor does following things
1.User may opens file with commond line argument orelse you may also open any file inside while text editor is running.
2.The opened file can be edited.
3.And user may save the edited file or else can exit text editor withoout saving.
4.It has following functionalities..

CTRL_O - open a file
CTRL_W - save a file
CTRL_X - cut a string
CTRL_B - copy a string
CTRL_V - paste the cut/copied string
CTRL_R - replace the string with some another string
CTRL_E - exit from the text editor
CTRL_D - delete line

